---
// HowWeHelp.astro - How We Help section showcasing FiNAN's main service areas
---

<section class="bg-gray-50 py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-6">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="motion-fade-up mb-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 md:text-5xl">
        Our Advocacy
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
        FiNAN supports Filipino nurses in the Nordics through guidance,
        advocacy, and community building. Explore our main focus areas and find
        resources tailored to your needs.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Cards Grid -->
    <div
      class="motion-stagger-children grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-3"
      data-motion-stagger="0.16"
    >
      <!-- Licensing Guidance Card -->
      <div
        class="block rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 transition-all hover:border-blue-900 hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        <img
          src="/assets/icons/advocacy_b-licensing-guidance.svg"
          alt="Licensing Guidance icon"
          class="mb-3 h-8 w-8"
        />
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
          Licensing Guidance
        </h3>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
          Get step-by-step support for obtaining or renewing your Nordic RN
          license, tailored to each country's specific requirements. FiNAN
          provides clear, reliable information to help you navigate the process
          with confidence.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Cultural Integration Card -->
      <div
        class="block rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 transition-all hover:border-blue-900 hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        <img
          src="/assets/icons/advocacy_b-cultural-integration.svg"
          alt="Cultural Integration icon"
          class="mb-3 h-8 w-8"
        />
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
          Cultural Integration
        </h3>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
          Receive dedicated support to help you adapt and thrive in life across
          the Nordic region. FiNAN offers resources for learning the local
          language, understanding cultural norms, and connecting with community
          networks.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Policy Advocacy Card -->
      <div
        class="block rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 transition-all hover:border-blue-900 hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        <img
          src="/assets/icons/advocacy_b-policy.svg"
          alt="Policy Advocacy icon"
          class="mb-3 h-8 w-8"
        />
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
          Policy Advocacy
        </h3>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
          We actively collaborate with government policymakers, hospitals,
          healthcare institutions, and universities to improve the recognition
          of Filipino nurses' qualifications and enhance their professional
          well-being.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
